{"tid":2031221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得同班收成期一齊攬炒，幾爽","createTime":"2020-05-23T09:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T10:43:11.000Z","uid":36775,"like":43,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"67bd3d8c95f549a79dac9d50a93d579a3ec8fd9c","tid":2031221,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"藍絲收成期因為利益<br />\n唔想有大風浪搞到自己資產跌價<br />\n而對中共惡行視而不見<br />\n佢地並唔會唔知支共衰野，我夠膽講<br />\n當中絕大部份支持過八九民運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只是因為錢、利益而埋沒良知<br />\n<br />\n佢地好多時有種思想<br />\n2047都已經七八十歲，都就死<br />\n一国一制對佢地影響唔大<br />\n有咩衰野等下一代自己承受<br />\n而家只不過將個時間線推前27年<br />\n等佢同我地一齊受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n某程度我覺得幾撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us"},{"pid":"7d87afcaa7e9519f13a65628ab5915d2ce5eecba","tid":2031221,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bf36b64ce6ed63c413e7fec00daebd7c8c1351","tid":2031221,"uid":194370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:10:45.000Z","msg":"其實係"},{"pid":"aa746ea8b6c90d2573d77ec4e9cffb1900daa266","tid":2031221,"uid":284855,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"第日佢地層未供斷的樓跌到仆街，工又冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcf88e3310121de6be01165ca47c8cae3900a76","tid":2031221,"uid":3860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3